"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Caves of Koilos\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Caves of Koilos\">Caves of Koilos</a> <br/>1x <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Terramorphic Expanse\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terramorphic Expanse\">Terramorphic Expanse</a> <br/> <br/>White (1):\r<br/>1x <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Enlightened Tutor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Enlightened Tutor\">Enlightened Tutor</a> <br/> <br/>Blue (20):\r<br/>4x ... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 190511)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '190511'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy43948\">Opeth2010</span>\r\n                                (8/24/2011 2:30:59 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/R